{"tid":576430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"狠心講分手 但最後傷嘅都係自己","createTime":"2018-03-01T01:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T15:26:31.000Z","uid":38058,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1922914d590c93d52c5555970529634fbab91da2","tid":576430,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"分開兩個月 先發現同佢嘅連繫少之又少<br />\n原來無揾對方 其實對佢平日生活一無所知<br />\n旁敲側擊一兩個共同識嘅朋友 得到嘅係佢對分手冇任何反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來從來得自己戇鳩鳩付出投入 連分手都對佢冇影響<br />\n感覺好似比人抹殺咗幾年黎嘅付出 存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都知佢唔放我係心上 分手都冇挽留<br />\n但惗唔到原來佢一啲唔開心都無 咁我地幾年黎算係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb4c150c525c7d67ca233efb8eafb4d11e99847","tid":576430,"uid":57962,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"946ad57f710993232184597478af9769cb2f5958","tid":576430,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb4c150c525c7d67ca233efb8eafb4d11e99847","tid":576430,"uid":57962,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"一齊幾年 點解可以放低得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec52408f937b71c7693202d1b5d8b94e361df9e0","tid":576430,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"634a7f18310ec8d87c5ff86aa2ce797adf14f828","tid":576430,"uid":83769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"946ad57f710993232184597478af9769cb2f5958","tid":576430,"uid":38058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb4c150c525c7d67ca233efb8eafb4d11e99847","tid":576430,"uid":57962,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"一齊幾年 點解可以放低